              "message" : "\nRESPONSE                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          \nSubject: Return Confirmation for Order #5019 - Smartphone Cord\n\nDear Eva Green,\n\nThank you for contacting us regarding your return. We're sorry to hear the box for your smartphone cord arrived damaged.\n\nWe have processed your return request for the following item:\n- Item: Smartphone Cord\n- Order Number: 5019\n- Reason: Box was broken\n\nAs requested, we will issue a full refund to the credit card on record once we receive and inspect the returned item. Please print the attached return shipping label, securely pack the smartphone cord, and ship it back to us at your earliest convenience.\n\nIf you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to reply to this email or contact us anytime.\n\nThank you for shopping with us!\n\nBest regards,  \nAlex Rivera  \nCustomer Return Agent  \nsupport@returns.com  \n1-800-RETURN-123    \n\n",
