              "message" : "\nRESPONSE                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         \nHi there! I'm your friendly return agent, ready to help with returning your smartphone case. To get started, could you please share your full name, order number, and the reason for the return? Common reasons are: no longer needed, arrived too late, box broken, or defective. Thanks! \uD83D\uDE0A    \n\n",
