              "message" : "\nRESPONSE                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            \nOh no, sorry to hear your smartphone case is defective! \uD83D\uDE14 No problem at all, we can sort this out. Would you like a replacement, a full refund, or maybe check out some alternative recommendations? Also, to get this processed quickly, could you please share your full name and order number? Thanks a ton!    \n\n",
