          "status" : "SUCCESS",
          "results" : [
            {
              "message" : "\nRESPONSE                                                                                                                                                                                                        \nSure thing! Here are two great alternative smartphone cases from our catalog that might suit you better:\n\n1. **TitanGuard Pro** ($34.50): Military-grade rugged case with reinforced corners, dust-proof port covers, matte anti-slip finish, and extreme drop protection. Perfect for outdoor adventures!\n\n2. **ArmorFlex Shield** ($29.99): Shock-absorbing TPU frame with scratch-resistant polycarbonate back for max impact protection, slim profile, and non-slip grip. Great balance of protection and sleekness!\n\nDo any of these catch your eye, or would you prefer to go with a replacement for the original or a full refund instead? Also, to process this, could you share your full name and order number? \uD83D\uDE0A    \n\n",
